com.martindengler.proj.FIXSimple

Class FIXStream

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.martindengler.proj.FIXSimple.FIXStream

  • public class FIXStream
extends java.lang.Object
    FIXStream encapulates a stream of FIXMessages going to / from a Reader / Writer endpoint.

    FIXStream ties together FIXStreamInputHandler and FIXStreamOutputHandler to read / write the bytes.

    Author:
    Martin Dengler
    See Also:
    FIXMessage, FIXStreamInputHandler, FIXStreamOutputHandler
